.Dd June 14, 2026
.Dt LIBVSBSDL 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm libvsbsdl.h
.Nd Library to access the BSD disklabel volume system format
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In libvsbsdl.h
.Pp
