.Fa "int codepage"
.Fa "libvsbsdl_error_t **error"
.Fc
.fi
.nf
.Ft int
.Fo libvsbsdl_check_volume_signature
.Fa "const char *filename"
.Fa "libvsbsdl_error_t **error"
.Fc
.fi
.Pp
Available when compiled with wide character string support:
.nf
.Ft int
.Fo libvsbsdl_check_volume_signature_wide
.Fa "const wchar_t *filename"
.Fa "libvsbsdl_error_t **error"
.Fc
.fi
.Pp
Available when compiled with libbfio support:
.nf
